<h2>Choose your weapon set</h2>

<p>Enter as many weapons as you like, in order of hierarchy.</p>
<p>The number of weapons must be an odd number.</p>
<p>For 3 items, the first item will beat the second item, the second item will beat the third item, and the third item will beat your first item.</p>
<p>For any configuration of size n, each item will beat the next n-1/2 items, with the same kind of circular logic</p>

<form action="/generate_rules_instance" method="post">
  <input class="button" type="text" name="weapons[]" value="rock">
  <input class="button" type="text" name="weapons[]" value="paper">
  <input class="button" type="text" name="weapons[]" value="scissors">
  <div id="more_options"></div>
  <input id="two_more" class="button" type="button" value="Add two more options">
  <br>
  <input class="button" type="submit" value="Submit">
</form>

